data.description: Stunning waterfront home on the beautiful Piankatank River with pier. 3 large bedrooms with an additional room and 3 full bathrooms. Large working kitchen with island, pantry and eating area. Extra large great room with brick fireplace and gas logs. A morning rooms sits behind the fireplace with access to the covered deck. Living room steps down to a large glassed Sun Room which goes out to the front porch. The room upstairs will make an excellent office, media room, or game room or an extra bedroom. The county is showing it has a 3 bedroom septic. The two car garage is extra large and room for a workshop area. Detached shed for your lawn equipment. Home has recently been professional upgraded to include new HVAC system with attached dehumidifier under the house. New HE Samsung washer and dryer. All rooms have been painted. All floors and cabinets cleaned and polished. Front porch painted and side entry areas. Home has a Home Warranty with 7 months left on warranty for the new owner.
